<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book"><i>The Modernist Papers</i>. London &amp; New York Verso. 2007.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Modernist+Papers&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft.pub=London+%26+New+York+Verso&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Fredric_Jameson"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book"><i>Jameson on Jameson: Conversations on Cultural Marxism</i>. Durham, NC: Duke University Press. 2007.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Jameson+on+Jameson%3A+Conversations+on+Cultural+Marxism&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft.pub=Durham%2C+NC%3A+Duke+University+Press&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Fredric_Jameson"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book"><i>Valences of the Dialectic</i>. London &amp; New York: Verso. 2009.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Valences+of+the+Dialectic&amp;rft.date=2009&amp;rft.pub=London+%26+New+York%3A+Verso&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Fredric_Jameson"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
</ul>
